# https://w3id.org/ficr#aboutElement
<https://w3id.org/ficr#aboutElement> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#aboutElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#BoundaryConditionRecord> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#aboutElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#PhysicalObject> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#aboutElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a boundary condition record to the physical object whose fire-related boundary or performance condition it concerns."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#aboutElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "aboutElement"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#appliesToElementType
<https://w3id.org/ficr#appliesToElementType> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#appliesToElementType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#RegulatoryRequirement> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#appliesToElementType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Specifies the class of physical element this requirement applies to, e.g. ficr:Wall or ficr:Floor."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#appliesToElementType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "appliesToElementType"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#appliesToPurposeGroup
<https://w3id.org/ficr#appliesToPurposeGroup> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#appliesToPurposeGroup> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#RegulatoryRequirement> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#appliesToPurposeGroup> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#PurposeGroup> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#appliesToPurposeGroup> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Specifies the building purpose group for which this requirement is applicable."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#appliesToPurposeGroup> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "appliesToPurposeGroup"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#appliesToRiskUnit
<https://w3id.org/ficr#appliesToRiskUnit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#appliesToRiskUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#BoundaryConditionRecord> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#appliesToRiskUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#RiskUnit> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#appliesToRiskUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a boundary condition record to the risk unit whose fire risk interpretation it informs."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#appliesToRiskUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "appliesToRiskUnit"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#assessesElement
<https://w3id.org/ficr#assessesElement> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#assessesElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#Assessment> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#assessesElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#PhysicalObject> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#assessesElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an assessment to the physical element(s) it evaluates. For compliance assessments, this is the wall, door, or floor being checked. For risk assessments, this covers elements involved in fire spread modelling."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#assessesElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "assessesElement"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#assessesZone
<https://w3id.org/ficr#assessesZone> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#assessesZone> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#Assessment> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#assessesZone> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/bot#Zone> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#assessesZone> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an assessment to the zone(s) or space(s) it covers. For risk assessments, this is the space whose fire scenario is being evaluated. For compliance assessments, this is the space containing the assessed elements."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#assessesZone> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "assessesZone"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#checksRequirement
<https://w3id.org/ficr#checksRequirement> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#checksRequirement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#ComplianceFinding> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#checksRequirement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#RegulatoryRequirement> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#checksRequirement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a compliance finding to the regulatory requirement being checked."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#checksRequirement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "checksRequirement"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsElement
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsElement> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#AssessmentFinding> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#PhysicalObject> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an assessment finding to the physical object it concerns."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsElement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "concernsElement"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsRiskUnit
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsRiskUnit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsRiskUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#AssessmentFinding> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsRiskUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#RiskUnit> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsRiskUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an assessment finding to the risk unit it concerns."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsRiskUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "concernsRiskUnit"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsSystem
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsSystem> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#AssessmentFinding> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#BuildingSystem> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an assessment finding to the building system it concerns."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "concernsSystem"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsZone
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsZone> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsZone> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#AssessmentFinding> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsZone> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/bot#Zone> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsZone> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an assessment finding to the spatial zone or space it concerns."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#concernsZone> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "concernsZone"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#containsSystem
<https://w3id.org/ficr#containsSystem> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#containsSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/ficr#isSystemContainedIn> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#containsSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/bot#Zone> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#containsSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#BuildingSystem> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#containsSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates a spatial zone to a building system located in, passing through, or spatially associated with that zone. This property is used where a system-level entity should not be treated as a BOT element."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#containsSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "containsSystem"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#coversSpatialZone
<https://w3id.org/ficr#coversSpatialZone> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#coversSpatialZone> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#RiskUnit> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#coversSpatialZone> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/bot#Zone> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#coversSpatialZone> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a risk unit to the spatial zone whose fire exposure it aggregates."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#coversSpatialZone> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "coversSpatialZone"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#dependsOnBoundaryCondition
<https://w3id.org/ficr#dependsOnBoundaryCondition> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#dependsOnBoundaryCondition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#FireRiskScenario> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#dependsOnBoundaryCondition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#BoundaryConditionRecord> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#dependsOnBoundaryCondition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a fire risk scenario to boundary condition records or assumptions that influence the scenario interpretation."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#dependsOnBoundaryCondition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "dependsOnBoundaryCondition"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#derivedFromRegulatorySource
<https://w3id.org/ficr#derivedFromRegulatorySource> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#derivedFromRegulatorySource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#RegulatoryRequirement> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#derivedFromRegulatorySource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#RegulatorySource> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#derivedFromRegulatorySource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a regulatory requirement individual to the regulatory, standard, or guidance source from which it was derived."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#derivedFromRegulatorySource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "derivedFromRegulatorySource"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#derivedFromScenario
<https://w3id.org/ficr#derivedFromScenario> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#derivedFromScenario> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#RiskFinding> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#derivedFromScenario> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#FireRiskScenario> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#derivedFromScenario> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a risk finding to the fire risk scenario from which it was derived, enabling finding-level traceability when one risk analysis evaluates multiple scenarios."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#derivedFromScenario> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "derivedFromScenario"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#hasApplicabilityState
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasApplicabilityState> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasApplicabilityState> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#AssessmentFinding> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasApplicabilityState> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#ApplicabilityState> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasApplicabilityState> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Records whether an assessment finding or checklist item is applicable, not applicable, or not assessed in the current assessment scope."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasApplicabilityState> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "hasApplicabilityState"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#hasAssessmentBasis
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasAssessmentBasis> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
