<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasAssessmentBasis> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an assessment activity or assessment result to the evidence bundle that supports it."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasAssessmentBasis> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "hasAssessmentBasis"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#hasBoundaryPerformanceAspect
