<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasBoundaryPerformanceAspect> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Identifies the boundary-related performance aspect assessed by a boundary condition record."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasBoundaryPerformanceAspect> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "hasBoundaryPerformanceAspect"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#hasClassification
