<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasClassification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "General property relating an entity to its classification."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasClassification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "hasClassification"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#hasComplianceResult
