<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasComplianceResult> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a compliance finding to its compliance result."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasComplianceResult> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "hasComplianceResult"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#hasComponent
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasComponent> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
