<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#PhysicalObject> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Expressing the compositional relationship of components"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasComponent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "hasComponent"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#hasConditionState
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasConditionState> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasConditionState> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#BoundaryConditionRecord> .
