<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasPurposeGroup> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#PurposeGroup> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasPurposeGroup> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates a building to its functional purpose group classification according to ADB Table 0.1"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasPurposeGroup> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "hasPurposeGroup"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#hasScenario
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasScenario> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasScenario> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#RiskAnalysis> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasScenario> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#FireRiskScenario> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasScenario> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a risk analysis to the fire risk scenario or scenarios it evaluates. Each scenario represents a hypothetical fire origin and relevant spread or exposure context used for risk-informed interpretation."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasScenario> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "hasScenario"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#hasScenarioRiskUnit
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasScenarioRiskUnit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasScenarioRiskUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#FireRiskScenario> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasScenarioRiskUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#RiskUnit> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasScenarioRiskUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a fire risk scenario to the risk unit whose fire risk is being interpreted."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasScenarioRiskUnit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "hasScenarioRiskUnit"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#hasSeparationRecord
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasSeparationRecord> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
