<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasSeparationRecord> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a risk unit to a separation distance record describing its exposure to an adjacent risk unit."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasSeparationRecord> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "hasSeparationRecord"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasSeparationRecord> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Informational: for future use."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#hasSpaceUsage
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasSpaceUsage> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasSpaceUsage> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ficr#hasUsageType> .
