<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasSpaceUsage> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/bot#Zone> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasSpaceUsage> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#SpaceUsage> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasSpaceUsage> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Assigns an everyday or operational space-use classification to a spatial zone or space, such as kitchen, corridor, lobby, bathroom, habitable room, or place of special hazard."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasSpaceUsage> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "hasSpaceUsage"@en .
# 
