<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasUtilizationPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ficr#hasUsageType> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#hasUtilizationPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/ficr#isUtilizationPurposeOf> .
