# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#producesEvidence
<https://w3id.org/ficr#producesEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#producesEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#Task> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#producesEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#EvidenceItem> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#producesEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a task to evidence items it generates."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#producesEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "producesEvidence"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#producesFinding
<https://w3id.org/ficr#producesFinding> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#producesFinding> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#Assessment> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#producesFinding> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#AssessmentFinding> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#producesFinding> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an assessment to the findings it produces."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#producesFinding> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "producesFinding"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#reliesOnBoundaryCondition
<https://w3id.org/ficr#reliesOnBoundaryCondition> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#reliesOnBoundaryCondition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#Assessment> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#reliesOnBoundaryCondition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#BoundaryConditionRecord> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#reliesOnBoundaryCondition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an assessment to a boundary condition record that it relies on or interprets. This allows compliance checking and risk analysis to expose whether their conclusions depend on effective, compromised, unknown, or weakly evidenced boundary conditions."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#reliesOnBoundaryCondition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "reliesOnBoundaryCondition"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#supportedByEvidence
<https://w3id.org/ficr#supportedByEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#supportedByEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#EvidenceItem> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#supportedByEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an assessment finding, boundary condition record, or other assessment-related record to evidence items that support, justify, or document it. The domain is intentionally left open because evidence support is used both for produced findings and for assessment dependencies such as boundary condition records."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#supportedByEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "supportedByEvidence"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#triggeredBy
<https://w3id.org/ficr#triggeredBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#triggeredBy> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/ficr#triggersTask> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#triggeredBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#Task> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#triggeredBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#Event> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#triggeredBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A task is created because an event (e.g., risk detected) occurred."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#triggeredBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "triggeredBy"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#triggersTask
<https://w3id.org/ficr#triggersTask> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#triggersTask> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#Event> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#triggersTask> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#Task> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#triggersTask> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a trigger event to the task(s) created because of it."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#triggersTask> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "triggersTask"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#usesComplianceFinding
<https://w3id.org/ficr#usesComplianceFinding> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#usesComplianceFinding> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#RiskAnalysis> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#usesComplianceFinding> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#ComplianceFinding> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#usesComplianceFinding> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a risk analysis to compliance findings used as inputs for risk interpretation."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#usesComplianceFinding> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "usesComplianceFinding"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#usesEvidence
<https://w3id.org/ficr#usesEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#usesEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/ficr#Task> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#usesEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/ficr#EvidenceItem> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#usesEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a task to evidence items it consumes as inputs."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#usesEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "usesEvidence"@en .
