<https://w3id.org/ficr#AutomaticReleaseMechanism> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A device that normally holds a door open, but closes it automatically if any one of the following occurs.\r\n• Smoke is detected by an automatic device of a suitable nature and quality in a suitable location.\r\n• A hand-operated switch, fitted in a suitable position, is operated.\r\n• The electricity supply to the device, apparatus or switch fails.\r\n• The fire alarm system, if any, is operated."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#AutomaticReleaseMechanism> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "AutomaticReleaseMechanism"@en .
