<https://w3id.org/ficr#BoundaryAssumption> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A boundary condition record used where risk analysis relies on an assumed, incomplete, or provisionally assessed boundary-performance condition. It may later be confirmed, revised, or replaced by inspection evidence."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#BoundaryAssumption> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "BoundaryAssumption"@en .
