<https://w3id.org/ficr#BoundaryPerformanceAspect> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A classification of the boundary-related performance aspect considered in fire risk interpretation, such as compartmentation, cavity barrier performance, external fire spread, or structural stability."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#BoundaryPerformanceAspect> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "BoundaryPerformanceAspect"@en .
