_:genid50 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty> <https://w3id.org/ficr#hasSystemFireSafetyRole> .
_:genid50 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Restriction> .
