<https://w3id.org/ficr#Roof> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/ficr#FabricElement> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#Roof> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A roof is the top covering of a building that provides protection from the elements like rain, sun, snow, and wind."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#Roof> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Roof"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/ficr#RoofSlab
