<https://w3id.org/ficr#RoofSpace> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A roof space is the area inside a building between the ceiling of the top floor and the underside of the roof."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#RoofSpace> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "RoofSpace"@en .
