<https://w3id.org/ficr#RooflightOpening> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A skylight, glazed barrel vault or other element to admit daylight through a roof."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#RooflightOpening> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "RooflightOpening"@en .
