<https://w3id.org/ficr#RoutineTriggerEvent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A trigger event generated from routine schedules or planned inspection cycles derived from FiCR maintenance and regulatory schedules, such as monthly fire exit checks."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#RoutineTriggerEvent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "RoutineTriggerEvent"@en .
