<https://w3id.org/ficr#Sensor> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A sensor in a building is a device that detects environmental changes and sends data to a control system to manage building functions like lighting, HVAC, and safety."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#Sensor> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Sensor"@en .
