<https://w3id.org/ficr#SiteBoundary> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A spatial boundary representing the extent of the site or land associated with a building. This class is not used to represent fire compartment boundaries or boundary condition records."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#SiteBoundary> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "SiteBoundary"@en .
