<https://w3id.org/ficr#UsageType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A controlled classification value used to assign use, purpose, or fire-safety role to buildings, spaces, physical objects, zones, or systems. UsageType values are used as controlled vocabulary terms and may be represented through OWL punning where required for value-based class definitions."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#UsageType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "UsageType"@en .
# 
