<https://w3id.org/ficr#UtilizationPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/ficr#UsageType> .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#UtilizationPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Assigns the planning or occupancy use of a building, such as dwellinghouse, office, hotel, school, shop, or factory. This is distinct from regulatory purpose group classification."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#UtilizationPurpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "UtilizationPurpose"@en .
