<https://w3id.org/ficr#VerticalTransportSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A Vertical Transport System (VT) in buildings refers to the equipment and planning used to move people and goods vertically between different floors."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ficr#VerticalTransportSystem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "VerticalTransportSystem"@en .
